				\begin{document}$$L_b$$\end{document}</tex-math><mml:math id="M16"><mml:msub><mml:mi>L</mml:mi><mml:mi>b</mml:mi></mml:msub></mml:math><inline-graphic xlink:href="12859_2024_5711_Article_IEq8.gif"/></alternatives></inline-formula>-variate generalized beta distribution, denoted by <inline-formula id="IEq9"><alternatives><tex-math id="M17">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
