      <p id="Par24">Consistent with the simulation study in Fig. <xref rid="Fig2" ref-type="fig">2</xref>, gbdmr is more sensitive than dmrff in identifying highly correlated DMRs in the real data analysis. Due to the block segmentation algorithm, gbdmr only identifies DMRs with neighboring DMR CpG’s correlation <inline-formula id="IEq63"><alternatives><tex-math id="M129">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
